INSERT INTO `articles_mask` (`post`,`native_id`,`post_account_id`,`post_type`) VALUES ("“They will be around a significant number of people – some of whom may be infectious,” said Dr. John Whyte, the chief medical officer of the health care website WebMD, to Fox News.µ<br/><br/> “It will be critically important that everyone follows safeguards [such as] absolutely wearing a mask, physical distancing and frequent handwashing.µThey should try to minimize any physical contact with people who come to vote.µFor instance, the public can simply show poll workers their ID rather than handing it to them,” he continued.µ<br/><br/> Whyte also suggested that voting places use plexiglass barriers between workers and voters, and noted that polling should “try to be in spaces with windows or doors open.”","1757504870","1","2");
